title: Ore wa Otoko da! Kunio-kun
original_name: おれは男だ! くにおくん
sinopse:
In a school of delinquents, there's one student that hates guys who pick on the weak, and his name is Kunio. He's as strong as they come, but unfortunately he's also lazy and perverted. Can Kunio win all of his challenges and survive the crazy antics of his opponents?

(Source: MU)
